Package edu.sjsu.cs151.spaceinvader.controller

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Valve
    Part of COMMAND design pattern implementation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Controller class that handles communication between View and Model as well as handle the state of the game.
    KeyPressedValve
    Valve that processes the Key Pressed event message by using the Board's set key down method and setting the appropriate flags for shot and bomb.
    KeyReleasedValve
    Valve that processes Key Released event message by using the Board's set key up method and updating.
    NewGameValve
    Valve to process New Game message, initates start over command and creates new aliens and resets speed and visibility.
    ViewUpdateValve
    Valve to process the View Update message sent by View during repaint.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Valve.ValveResponse
